🔹 Minterm Numbering (VERY IMPORTANT)

For variables A,B:

A	B	Minterm	Index
0	0	A'B'	m₀
0	1	A'B	m₁
1	0	AB'	m₂
1	1	AB	m₃

📌 Index is binary value.

🔹 K-Map (Karnaugh Map)

Used for visual simplification.

🔹 2-Variable K-Map

4 cells

🔹 3-Variable K-Map

8 cells

🔹 4-Variable K-Map

16 cells

🔹 K-Map Rules (VERY IMPORTANT)

1️⃣ Group sizes must be power of 2:

1, 2, 4, 8...

2️⃣ Groups must be rectangular

3️⃣ Wrap-around allowed (edges connect)

4️⃣ Make largest possible groups

🔹 Types of Grouping

Pair → removes 1 variable

Quad → removes 2 variables

Octet → removes 3 variables

🔹 Don’t Care Conditions

