Helps in simplification

📌 Very common GATE questions.

🔹 SOP vs POS (Exam Point)
SOP	POS
Uses minterms	Uses maxterms
OR of AND terms	AND of OR terms
K-map grouping of 1s	K-map grouping of 0s
🔹 Important GATE Traps

Missing wrap-around grouping

Not choosing largest group

Ignoring don’t-care optimization

